OL,7,FThe report warned of a "pincer
OL,8,Fmovement of abandonment and
OL,9,Fgentrification" which has gradually
OL,10,Fseen community spaces, such as the
OL,11,FSouthport pier which closed in 2022,
OL,12,Flost and increased isolation of people
OL,13,Fin many areas.
OL,15,FReferring to previous research, the
OL,16,Freport said 50 UK pubs close for good
OL,17,Feach month, an estimated 600 youth
OL,18,Fclubs shut between 2012 and 2016 and
OL,19,FLondon lost almost 10 local authority-
OL,20,Frun community spaces a year between
OL,21,F2018 and 2023.
