OL,8,Fwelfare fund" raised through a so-
OL,9,Fcalled Amazon tax, whereby warehouses
OL,10,Fand distribution centres are subject
OL,11,Fto higher levies or online sales taxes.
OL,13,FIt argued online retailers which build
OL,14,F"giant structures" ` a demonstration
OL,15,Fof their high value ` often do not
