OL,8,F#1 million could help generate
OL,9,F"larger, more sustained resource for
OL,10,Fcommunities than current community
OL,11,Fregeneration efforts", it said.
OL,13,FThe report said: "If there is a thread
OL,14,Fconnecting the high-octane events of
OL,15,Flate July (2024) and the slow local
OL,16,Fpolitics of the pier, it is the loss
OL,17,Fof physical spaces where we might come
OL,18,Ftogether, and the radicalisation of
OL,19,Fsome of the digital spaces that have
OL,20,Freplaced them.
