OL,7,FReport author Dr Sacha Hilhorst said:
OL,8,F"The Southport riots were a wake-up
OL,9,Fcall ` a stark reminder of what can
OL,10,Fhappen when communities lose the
OL,11,Fplaces that once brought people
OL,12,Ftogether. In the absence of shared
OL,13,Fspaces, misinformation and hate can
OL,14,Ffill the void, creating tinderbox
OL,15,Fconditions for violence.
OL,17,F"Rebuilding local infrastructure isn't
OL,18,Fjust about nostalgia ` it's a vital
OL,19,Fbulwark against division and the
OL,20,Fdangerous pull of the far right.
