OL,7,F"But communities are not apathetic.
OL,8,FThey are crying out for places to
OL,9,Fgather, to organise, and to belong. We
OL,10,Fneed a new generation of institutions
OL,11,Fto help them do just that."
OL,13,FDr Parth Patel, associate director at
OL,14,Fthe IPPR, said: "Where shared spaces
OL,15,Fare lost, a sense of decline and
OL,16,Fdisconnection takes root ` and with
OL,17,Fit, dangerous alternatives thrive.
